Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.98,0:00:05.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At last, the time has come...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.90,0:00:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.07,0:00:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show 'em what you learned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.90,0:00:11.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go for a flawless victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.66,0:00:15.66,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,A Seductress\Nin Disguise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.03,0:00:15.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for the love of God,\Nget that woman far away from me...!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.66,0:00:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Begin!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.58,0:00:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Attaboy, Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.75,0:00:28.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to our training...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.71,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They oughtta be on equal footing now
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:34.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, his skills are bound \Nto have surpassed hers!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She's laughing...?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.22,0:00:40.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why's Spartokos moving so slow...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.35,0:00:43.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.39,0:00:47.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is she using her boobs to distract him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:48.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.81,0:00:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Try as you might, you shall \Nnever defeat me in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.53,0:00:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was her boobs the whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.57,0:01:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.02,0:01:01.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Peter!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.49,0:01:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The match is over...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.34,0:01:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.20,0:01:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.09,0:01:13.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boing! Boing! Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.59,0:01:14.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously...?\NBoing! Boing! Boing!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.51,0:01:16.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Winner: Big Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.93,0:01:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Piece of cake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.59,0:01:19.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I call foul play!\NPiece of cake, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.18,0:01:21.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos is a virgin!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.97,0:01:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Swinging those giant udders\Nof yours around isn't fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't believe that this is a proper\Ntechnique for a soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.53,0:01:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A fight's a fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.06,0:01:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the big idea,\Ninsultin' us Ogres with your dumb accusations?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.86,0:01:36.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.74,0:01:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your efforts to lead a life of total\Ndiscipline cost you everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.74,0:01:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unfortunately, it would seem that this, too,\Nis the fate of the creature known as "man"...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.79,0:01:48.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You poor soul...!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.34,0:01:59.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.81,0:02:06.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.14,0:02:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Back against the wall... I \Nmean, how could I resist?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.40,0:02:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"This wasn't supposed to \Nhappen," I keep denying
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.65,0:02:21.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could just disappear... \NI can't stand myself
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.87,0:02:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Moping around, spouting lies, \Ngrieving a broken heart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.33,0:02:28.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hold on desperately to these \Nfeelings and shut my eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.50,0:02:31.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So why does this stupid \Nguilt refuse to go away?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.75,0:02:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suffocate under its weight
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The chance to be a hero is long gone...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.47,0:02:42.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Always discouraged by my weaknesses,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.72,0:02:45.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I drop to my knees and grovel at your feet,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.93,0:02:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,clinging selfishly to \Nthe hope for forgiveness
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dug myself into a hole with no way out...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.23,0:02:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Full of regret and powerless to change,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.48,0:02:58.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel my heart being torn apart
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.74,0:03:02.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,on this night of endless shame and despair
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.45,0:03:11.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why can't I get my act together?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.63,0:03:17.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got nothing but this pathetic self of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:24.35,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Episode 12: Peter Grill and \Nthe Warrior that Shouted Love
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.13,0:03:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-The duel...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.97,0:03:27.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bad news, my friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.02,0:03:29.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It cannot be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.44,0:03:31.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have lost yet again...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.60,0:03:33.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:38.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if he were to demand another rematch,\NI doubt the outcome would be any different.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.28,0:03:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,His combat skills aren't the problem...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C-Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.99,0:03:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,E-Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.54,0:03:50.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is Spartokos-san awake yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.41,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitchie Peregrym!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry for showing up out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.92,0:03:54.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait...\NUm, sorry for showing up out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.63,0:03:55.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Um, sorry for showing up out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.17,0:03:55.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the answer is obvious!\NUm, sorry for showing up out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.79,0:03:57.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come to think of it, the answer is obvious!\NI, uh, didn't startle you, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.21,0:03:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, uh, didn't startle you, did I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.13,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The missing piece of Spartokos' puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman... Woman...\NThe missing piece of Spartokos' puzzle...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.42,0:04:00.42,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,Woman
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling comfortable around women!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.05,0:04:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! I apologize for such a pathetic display...\NFeeling comfortable around women!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.55,0:04:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Not at all! I apologize for such a pathetic display...\NThat's all he needs!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.18,0:04:05.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.18,0:04:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos-kun, got a sec?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.26,0:04:13.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, listen... What do you \Nthink of Mitchie-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.56,0:04:16.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm afraid I don't understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.19,0:04:17.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Between you and me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.74,0:04:22.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mitchie's known for being a connoisseur\Nof guys with huge, rippling muscles.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.95,0:04:26.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And with an enticing physique like yours,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's safe to say that you'd\Nhave no problem winning her over...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:30.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.74,0:04:32.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you implying?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.69,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let me be frank: You aren't \Nable to beat Lisa...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.33,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...because you're far too susceptible\Nto the charms of the opposite sex!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.00,0:04:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wha-?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.17,0:04:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you just say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.09,0:04:47.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your obsession with remaining abstinent\Nfor Lisa's sake is a disadvantage.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.26,0:04:52.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your eyes wander across her body during battle,\Ndestroying your ability to concentrate!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.89,0:04:56.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you need to build up\Nmore experience with women!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.02,0:05:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What exactly are you \Nsuggesting I do, Sir Peter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:04.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You would have me surrender my virginity\Nto a woman other than Lady Lisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:06.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I-I mean, think about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whenever Mitchie was around...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:12.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spending time with her gave you\Nbutterflies in your stomach, didn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.08,0:05:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nevertheless, I-I have devoted \Nmy entire life to Lady Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.88,0:05:21.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have sacrificed every \Nwaking moment for her!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.33,0:05:22.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.46,0:05:24.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That way of thinking isn't healthy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.84,0:05:28.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're depriving yourself of other possibilities because
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.34,0:05:31.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're way too focused on chasing after this one woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.64,0:05:34.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is connected \Ndirectly to your weaknesses!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.48,0:05:36.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,B-But...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.36,0:05:37.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spartokos-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.61,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Mitchie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.36,0:05:40.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nice!\NLady Mitchie?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.36,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening this whole time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.61,0:05:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You care deeply for Lisa-san, \Nand I'm fully aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.07,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.58,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I, too... perhaps just as deeply...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.58,0:05:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...feel the same way about you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.13,0:06:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Mitchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.51,0:06:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the walls surrounding that\Ninnocent heart of his were paper-thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.01,0:06:08.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the walls surrounding that\Ninnocent heart of his were paper-thin.\NLady Mitchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.22,0:06:09.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the walls surrounding that\Ninnocent heart of his were paper-thin.\NSir Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.64,0:06:10.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the walls surrounding that\Ninnocent heart of his were paper-thin.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.14,0:06:10.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like the walls surrounding that\Ninnocent heart of his were paper-thin.\NLady Mitchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he needed was a little push.\NLady Mitchie...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.05,0:06:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All he needed was a little push.\NSir Spartokos...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.81,0:06:15.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have nothing left to teach you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.14,0:06:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fare thee well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.85,0:06:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lady Mitchie...\NFare thee well.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sir Peter...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.58,0:06:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For some strange reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.79,0:06:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel as though a burden\Nhas been lifted from my shoulders.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.87,0:06:41.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yup, you're a changed man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.00,0:06:44.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Totally different than the \Nperson you were yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.59,0:06:46.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that power coursing through your veins...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.82,0:06:50.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It should be more than enough \Nto defeat Lisa Alpacas!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.80,0:06:54.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go request another rematch right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sir Peter...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.56,0:06:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I must admit, it was exactly as you said.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.72,0:07:01.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By pouring my time and effort into\Nthe pursuit of a particular woman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had lost sight of the \Npath to true happiness.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.23,0:07:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.82,0:07:08.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tokos~!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.65,0:07:10.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Mitchie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.03,0:07:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, you forgot your lunch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.38,0:07:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How thoughtful of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.94,0:07:17.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eat this, and tonight you'll \Nhave more muscles, muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.65,0:07:18.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles, muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.08,0:07:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, hello...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.91,0:07:22.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What about your rematch with Lisa...?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:23.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Lady Lisa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.39,0:07:25.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Lisa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.30,0:07:28.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all water under the bridge now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.26,0:07:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tokos, you should join our Guild, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.05,0:07:33.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Goddammit...!\NHey Tokos, you should join our Guild, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.09,0:07:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey Tokos, you should join our Guild, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.51,0:07:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.72,0:07:35.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy gave up as soon as he got a girlfriend!\NI suppose so...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.39,0:07:36.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The guy gave up as soon \Nas he got a girlfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:41.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could've sworn everything was\Ngoing according to plan...!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a relief...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.90,0:07:46.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It would appear that he's finally \Nfound a suitable partner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.05,0:07:47.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lisa?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.57,0:07:49.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.11,0:07:49.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite his sentimental nature,\Nthat man is the best our army has to offer.\NMuscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.53,0:07:50.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite his sentimental nature,\Nthat man is the best our army has to offer.\NMuscles?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.65,0:07:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite his sentimental nature,\Nthat man is the best our army has to offer.\NMuscles, muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.03,0:07:52.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Despite his sentimental nature,\Nthat man is the best our army has to offer.\NMuscles! Muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.78,0:07:53.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Muscles! Muscles!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's a top-notch soldier \Nand a capable leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.57,0:07:59.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I expect that this situation will dispel\Nany doubts and encourage success.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.95,0:08:04.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you a debt of gratitude for your\Nassistance with this matter, Peter Grill.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.17,0:08:07.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The path to happiness..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.59,0:08:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't have said it better myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.13,0:08:14.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you considered giving any thought to it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.43,0:08:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What does "true happiness" mean to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.06,0:08:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marrying that naïve, oblivious Luvellia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.27,0:08:29.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Getting stuck with that senile old\NAlbatross as your father-in-law?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be honest.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.73,0:08:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that what you'd call "true happiness"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.51,0:08:34.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-Well, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.95,0:08:38.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you were serious about our relationship...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.58,0:08:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's a possibility that you could\Nbecome the king of an entire nation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.00,0:08:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What'd she just say...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.42,0:08:47.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it over carefully.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.84,0:08:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Which path is it you seek?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.80,0:08:53.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where does your true happiness lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.26,0:08:59.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"True happiness..."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.26,0:09:00.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.02,0:09:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.86,0:09:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I already told myself that \NI'm done being indecisive!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.28,0:09:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.61,0:09:17.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.78,0:09:20.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My mind is made up...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.41,0:09:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that this is my path to happiness!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.20,0:09:25.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.62,0:09:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luvellia-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.87,0:09:28.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where have you been?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.29,0:09:30.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, you have to come with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.04,0:09:31.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the Goblins!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.26,0:09:32.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.05,0:09:33.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,N-No way...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.08,0:09:36.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Goblin Invasion is finally upon us!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.26,0:09:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A feeding frenzy of despicable creatures called\NGoblins who devour every man in sight...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.35,0:09:47.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've already received numerous requests\Nfor backup from villages across the area!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.02,0:09:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A mass outbreak of Goblins...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.57,0:09:52.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we don't nip this in the bud,\Nthe effects could be catastrophic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.90,0:09:54.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I just hope we make it in time...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.32,0:09:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look out, Luvellia-senpai!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.70,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't mind going on a trip together\Noutside of our Guild duties.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.20,0:10:05.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the two of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.79,0:10:08.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll protect you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.25,0:10:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what happens, I'll keep you safe!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.96,0:10:15.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Same here. I have faith in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.30,0:10:19.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When this mission is over, \Nit's just you and me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.28,0:10:21.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait to go on vacation together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.89,0:10:24.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Agape!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.10,0:10:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meet Agape Jr.!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.92,0:10:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,91 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.35,0:10:30.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this, amateur hour?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.73,0:10:31.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.48,0:10:34.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A woman admired by Sir Peter \Nisn't to be trifled with!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.78,0:10:35.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.65,0:10:38.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our record still stands at over 100 points!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.49,0:10:42.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Losing to Albatross' foolish \Ndaughter is NOT an option!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.37,0:10:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Peter Grill, regardless of which\Npath you choose to take...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:53.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...those precious juices \Nof yours belong to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.71,0:10:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It started out as a simple crush
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.26,0:11:00.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly, you were my \Nbiggest source of strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.18,0:11:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Till death do us part, \Nlet's grow old together
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.97,0:11:06.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my sincerest wish:
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.22,0:11:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me, stay with me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.27,0:11:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long time, by my side for all eternity
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.82,0:11:14.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Beaten down by our daily struggles
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.98,0:11:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Or soaked by a storm of rage;
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.50,0:11:20.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you get drenched, I won't hesitate
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.28,0:11:22.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To be the umbrella that shields you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:25.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not so cold... I'm by your side
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's good enough for me
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.20,0:11:31.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.08,0:11:34.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That smile of yours puts my soul at ease
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.96,0:11:37.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I could search the whole world over
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.38,0:11:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And find no one like you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.47,0:11:42.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're my rock, my strength
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.47,0:11:46.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just the sight of you fills my heart with joy
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much it may hurt,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.60,0:11:52.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I pledge my life to protecting you
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.86,0:11:57.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dear Sir Peter Grill...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.73,0:12:03.03,On Top,,0000,0000,0000,,An Elite Squad of Hobgoblins\N"The Three Stars of Hell"
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.20,0:12:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like it's our turn next...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.28,0:12:08.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.29,0:12:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big Brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,